{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody gave me something to put on top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One of the women gave me something, because they heard, and they were all-- they were also impressed that I got a chance to go and sing for the head of the camp.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, when I got there, I sang for her all the love songs I remembered my sisters singing, and they were all very nice, and they took another girl along with me too.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was also from our hometown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was bigger than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody was bigger than me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, at least my own age, they were taller and bigger.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "By that time, I was already 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember, when she got through with me, she told me she was going to take me and get me dressed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I told her, I said, I would-- I need some clothes for my mother, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wouldn't want to be dressed-- I mean, I want her to have some clothes too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, needless to say, I don't know if a day passed by, or two, or three, or whatever time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She took me to the storeroom, where there were-- I can't tell you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was like going into a Paris shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You-- you can dress as you will.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- and they dressed me up like I walked out of a showroom, with a coat and a dress and shoes and stockings and god knows what.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I brought back for my mother shoes and clothes and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Well unfortunately, I don't know how long this lasted, but it was only like days before they took us out of that B lager.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They took the children and separated us completely and took us away.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
